# Redirecciones permanentes de matiascappato.com a cappato.dev
https://matiascappato.com/* https://cappato.dev/:splat 301!
https://www.matiascappato.com/* https://cappato.dev/:splat 301!

# Asegurar que www.cappato.dev redirija a cappato.dev (sin www)
https://www.cappato.dev/* https://cappato.dev/:splat 301!

# Blog URL cleanup - redirect malformed URLs to blog index
/blog/pillar/ /blog 301
/blog/tag/ /blog 301
/blog/tags/ /blog 301
/blog/tags /blog 301

# Force HTTPS for any HTTP requests
http://cappato.dev/* https://cappato.dev/:splat 301!

# Specific blog URL patterns that should redirect to blog index
/blog/post/* /blog 301
/blog/posts/* /blog 301
/blog/article/* /blog 301
/blog/articles/* /blog 301
/blog/category/* /blog 301
/blog/categories/* /blog 301
/blog/author/* /blog 301
/blog/authors/* /blog 301
/blog/archive/* /blog 301
/blog/search/* /blog 301

